title: Trump indictment is 'very, very damning,' his former attorney general says
description: Donald Trump's former Attorney General Bill Barr said Trump is "toast" after a 37-count criminal indictment against him was unsealed Friday.

title: Man City 1-0 Inter Milan: Rodri's goal wins Champions League final as Pep Guardiola's team complete treble

title: Longevity doctor shares the No. 1 diet he follows to 'beat diseases and live longer': It's a 'unique blend' of foods
description: Dr. William Li, a physician, food scientist and bestselling author, has spent 20 years studying how our diets can help us fight diseases and live longer. He shares his No. 1 longevity diet that keeps his body young, strong and healthy.
